<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 22:28:22 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>木台上的鞋</title><link>https://some.pics/69e405828fa06</link><description>&lt;p&gt;两双鞋子摆放在日本戸塚区户外环境的木制平台上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two pairs of shoes on a wooden deck in an outdoor setting, 戸塚区, Japan." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/rick/69e405828fa06.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://rick.some.pics"&gt;@rick&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 22:28:22 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>机器人Alpha的永恒孤独</title><link>https://some.pics/69e3f279c009a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我真的很喜欢《横滨购物纪行》漫画中的这一格。主角阿尔法小姐是一个一直独自生活的机器人。如今她与其他角色共度了这么多时光，他们却必须继续各自的人生旅程。她曾渴望独处，但现在她意识到自己也想成长。可悲的是，她永远不会变老，注定要看着他们渐渐老去……而自己却始终如一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A black and white manga-style illustration of a person's face and shoulders. The person has large eyes and hair with bangs, and is wearing a light-colored top with a bow at the collar. A speech bubble on the left reads, &amp;quot;THERE ARE PARTS OF MY BRAIN I CAN'T MOVE BY MYSELF.&amp;quot; A speech bubble on the right reads, &amp;quot;HOW DO I PUT IT...&amp;quot; A small cup is partially visible at the bottom of the frame." height="496" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dawn/69e3f279c009a.png" width="628"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dawn.some.pics"&gt;@dawn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 21:07:08 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>健身塑形</title><link>https://some.pics/69e3e90b390bc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;合适&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="yzy gap sateen cargo &amp;amp; BL-01" height="3002" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/selah/69e3e90b390bc.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://selah.some.pics"&gt;@selah&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 20:26:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>巴塞罗那</title><link>https://some.pics/69e3d6e23c70c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;巴塞罗那。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Looking up at three modern urban buildings in front of a bright blue sky. Direct afternoon sunlight is hitting them, accentuating their unique architectural characteristics" height="3264" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/69e3d6e23c70c.jpg" width="2448"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 19:09:25 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>机库一瞥</title><link>https://some.pics/69e3d5ff78574</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从一个飞机库。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Close-up of a well-used industrial aircraft mechanic machine, comprising lots of metal and wires of various shapes and styles. Blurred behind it are two airplane tires stacked on a drain on a concrete floor." height="1704" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/markwyner/69e3d5ff78574.jpg" width="2272"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://markwyner.some.pics"&gt;@markwyner&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 19:05:38 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>